snippet.title: The Sims 3 Into the Future Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
There's no need to fast forward, The Sims 3 Into the Future Launch Trailer is here! What will your Sims discover in the future? 

Pre-order the expansion pack now on Origin and get even more content with the Limited Edition Quantum Power Pack plus the Origin Exclusive Dark Industrial Set! http://bit.ly/FutureSims3
